high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge on your right
Remove the potato that is in the fridge
Turn around and find the white table behind you.
Set the potato down on the back right corner of the table
Turn to your right and walk forward to find the sink
Pick up the potato that is in the sink
Turn around and return to the table that you placed the previous potato on
Set the potato from the sink down underneath the potato you placed in step 4
anns.task_desc: Place two potatoes on the table

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the refrigerator on the right.

Turn around and reach the white table.
Put the potato on the right edge of the table.
Head to the sink on the right.
Pick the potato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Place the potato in front of the other potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two potatoes on the table.
